  "detailed_description": "Your kingdom has only one piece of land left, and the enemies seem determined not to spare you. How you rebuild a city in a limited time and defeat the powerful invaders depends on your choices.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build a defense system</h2>Construct several different types of defense towers or deploy your army to resist the enemy's attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424740/extras/7382d5bc6e92f598a603386620d87a2c.poster.avif?t=1709614854\" width=718 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424740/extras/7382d5bc6e92f598a603386620d87a2c.webm?t=1709614854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424740/extras/7382d5bc6e92f598a603386620d87a2c.mp4?t=1709614854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cards</h2>Every day, use randomly generated cards from a pool of over 100 different cards to construct the city, build defenses, establish barracks, and more.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424740/extras/f0cefa3d773f064d6ced3d832458dbbc.poster.avif?t=1709614854\" width=800 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424740/extras/f0cefa3d773f064d6ced3d832458dbbc.webm?t=1709614854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rich equipment system</h2>Choose from dozens of different equipment options that suit your game strategy to make the game more enjoyable and entertaining.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i